==Min Nan==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[ tui˥˧put˥˥tsu˧˧ ]}}

===Verb===
{{nan-verb|t|poj=tùi-pu̍t-chū|pojt=tui3put4chu7|tra=對不住|sim=对不住|rs=寸11}}

# to cause someone embarassment; to screw someone over; to do something to a person that would demand an apology later on

===Usage notes===
*'''tùi-put-chū''' is not used as an interjection meaning ''I'm sorry'' in Min Nan.  Use [[歹勢]] ([[phái-sè]]) or [[失禮]] ([[sit-lé]]) instead.

